 Hajiya Sadiya Umar, Minister of Humanitarian Affairs, Disaster Management and Social Development, has revalidated her membership of the All-Progressives Congress (APC) in Zamfara. Mrs Nneka Anibeze, Special Assistant to the Minister on Media, disclosed this in a statement on Monday in Abuja. Anibeze said that Umar was presented with her membership card by the state APC caretaker chairman, Alhaji Lawal Kaura. She said the ceremony was witnessed by dignitaries including party executives and elders among others. (NAN)